Description:
In a corner of the ruins you come across a group of suspicious-looking people.

As you approach you realise that they are placing bets among themselves while playing cards. When they see you, they invite you to join in with the chance to triple your bet if you win.
DescriptionAction: Do you feel like placing a bet?
